title: 401Health
description: 401Health provides Rhode Islanders with an easy way to track symptoms, find vaccine records, and learn about COVID-19 testing, treatment, and vaccination. All Rhode Islanders are encouraged to use the 401Health app and take an active role in slowing the spread of COVID-19 in Rhode Island. You can make a difference in the health of your loved ones and your community by helping us track the virus in our state. 401Health is a one-stop shop to get all the information you need about COVID-19 in Rhode Island. Please see our Terms of Use (https://health.ri.gov/covid/crush/termsofuse/) & Privacy Policy (https://health.ri.gov/covid/crush/privacypolicy/) for further information.
